description.249: The product you are buying is solid pine wood, made of Radiata pine. Radiata pine is an extremely strong wood, with a beautiful finish. Pine has a high resin content that gives it its strength, but can also cause slight blemishing in the finish. Knots, slight hairline cracks close to the knots, and small imperfections in the pine are part of the nature of this type of pine. Discovery World has stringent guidelines on the amount and size of knots that are located in areas where strength is of the utmost importance (bed rails, ladders, etc.). Some of these imperfections are caused by expansion and contraction due to environmental factors, and once in your home, will not worsen. Solid wood will not fail, even with extreme moisture, but one should expect to see minor acceptable defects due to the natural expansion and contraction of the product in a warehouse, in transit, and in your home. For those looking for a great fit, a deep natural finish, that may have natural imperfections but will last a lifetime, we recommend a solid wood product.

description.631: “We fidget to focus.” This, according to Formway Senior designer, was the central thesis that informed MultiGeneration by Knoll®. The shape and material of the shell give the chair a buoyancy that prevents the user from feeling “locked in” while the arm and leg positions allow for 270 degrees of movement. The optional hybrid base for MultiGeneration is a unique design solution that combines the comfort of a cantilever form with a sturdy four-leg construction, giving the option of mobility from casters and freeing up the front corners for various postures. Cantilevered chairs have dynamic frames that respond to a user’s weight, but typically they cannot accommodate casters, which are desirable in a multipurpose chair, nor do they have front leg structures that can limit the user’s leg movement. Four-leg chairs are sturdy and allow for casters, but they don’t have a dynamic frame. Formway selected the most desirable attributes of the traditional base types to create the MultiGeneration hybrid base, a melding of cantilever and four-leg constructions. MultiGeneration serves the functional purposes of a side chair, with the consideration and ergonomics of a standalone seating solution.

Features include foam padded tilting backrest, foam padded seat, armrests and rolling wheels. Ergonomic gas lift adjusts the seat to your body height and shape with ease. A great addition to any home!
description.880: This elegant office chair will add an upscale appearance to your office with its shiny ribbed upholstery. This chair was designed to support the lower-to-mid back region. Chair easily swivels 360 degrees to get the maximum use of your workspace without strain. The pneumatic adjustment lever will allow you to easily adjust the seat to your desired height. From behind the desk to the conference room, this chair can provide a seamless addition to your work space.
description.885: The only armchair on the market with two specific functions; In the upright position, a beautiful and comfortable executive desk chair. Once the footrest is activated, It converts instantly into a Lafer reclining chair, with all its incredible features. You buy one chair and get two: one for working and another for relaxing.
description.888: Traditional styling coupled with advanced control options. Classic crested back design with scalloped seat front. Fully upholstered outer back and arms.
description.889: Charles Pollock’s 1963 Executive Chair features what he described as “rim technology”— the use of a single aluminum band around the chair’s perimeter to hold the design together, structurally and visually. Fifty years after its introduction, the Pollock Chair continues to exude timeless elegance.
description.890: Style your home desk with the convenient chair featuring a black gloss form fitted seat and back rest, chromed gas lift and chromed legs with rolling wheels. The contemporary design will accent any desk setting while offering the option to adjust to your height with ease. A great addition to any home!
description.893: Be the leader of your desk with the Boutique Office Chair. Features leatherette wrapped seat and tufted back cushion with chrome frame. Adjustable height and tilt.
description.897: Versatile and comfortable, our Miller Office Chair features the same stylish compact profile for small and large office spaces.
description.901: Designed between 1995 and 1996, the Maui chair was the focus of design research in the nineties and is the first of a new generation of monocoque chairs made of a material without veins or ribs, metal supports, or any reinforcing frame to support the back. The elegant lines and its practicality make the Maui chair an extremely versatile design, just as up-to-date today as it was yesterday.
description.903: Add a class and style to your workplace by getting this Furinno Hidup Mid-Back Mesh Ergonomic Office Chair. Simple yet stunning to look at, this task chair enhances the look of your office with its presence. This task chair belongs to Hidup collection.The Hidup Mid-Back Mesh Ergonomic Office Chair from Furinno features a butterfly work plate padded mesh seat and low back that provides comfortable support to your back. With just one touch, you can adjust the height of this task chair with a pneumatic gas lift height adjuster. This task chair can be controlled for its tilt so you can conveniently adjust your seating position. The durable nylon casters enable you to move the task chair effortlessly around the workplace. The base of this chair is made of nylon. It is not only sturdy but also ensures solid stability. The beautifully designed backrest will complement the decor of your home or office. This Task chair can be arranged in front of your office desk or in your kid’s study or computer table. It is durable and will serve you for many years to come.The chair is easy to maintain and can be cleaned with a soft dry cloth to keep it clean and dust-free.
description.904: Ventilated Seating at it's best! chair features locking tilt controls in addition to adjustable tilt tension.
description.914: The Harding Game chair is a distinguished addition to any home. The chair displays many fine features found in collections costing twice the price. The rich cherry finish has a warm, glowing appeal. The chairs are covered in top grain brown leather with a button tuck design and accented with a stately nail head trim. The game chairs feature a full 360 degree swivel, locking tilt / riser mechanisms and heavy duty casters for increased comfort and mobility. All of these great features make this a gamble that is a sure thing.
description.916: The Mayline Comfort High-Back Office Chair with Arms is chair is designed with style, comfort, and durability in mind. This executive chair features a sophisticated design and looks sleek. The office chair provides a professional look to the office ambiance. It offers inflatable lumbar support and is the perfect choice for an orthopedic patient. This Comfort High-Back Office Chair with Arms by Mayline has deep cushioned seat, back, and headrest that are upholstered in high-quality leather or fabric. It has a swivel seat with pneumatic height adjustment, ensuring you are at ease while working even for long hours. The chair has a sturdy base and features five casters that promise ease at mobility. This office chair is made from premium materials and is sure to be a part of your office for years to come. The chair is available in various colors, so you can select the one that meets your styling requirements perfectly. It is easy to keep this office chair clean and tidy. Simply wipe it regularly with a clean, dry cloth, and this office chair will look as good as new. The chair has a weight limit of 500 pounds and can be easily assembled with the help of a screwdriver.
description.923: Contoured seat and back provide comfort for long hours of sitting.
description.924: At home in either traditional or contemporary setting,This can be an executive behind-the-desk chair, or beautiful option for conference room. Classic stitched piping on seat and back cushions and fully upholstered back give chair professional finished look. Understated pattern on fabric completes elegant appearance.
description.925: This office chair provides complete comfort to people sitting for long intervals. The breathable mesh back allows airflow to prevent sweating, and padded armrests flip up or down for your convenience. The nylon mesh fabric with high density soft foam padding cradles you in a state of relaxation. The durable Nylon Baking Varnish Base is made to last, with caster wheels for easy mobility. This is a classic chair that is stylish and comfortable, and will be right at home in your office.
description.927: The ergonomic chair that fits you and your budget!
description.929: The office chair puts in the driver's seat at work or at the home office. The chair blends sleek racecar-inspired styling with comfort. The chair has a sturdy alloy base with four legs for stability. The chair feels like a bucket seat in a race car. Settle in and enjoy the comfort of the bolstered chair with tire-embossed, padded armrests. The armrests are height adjustable. The chair is ergonomic for comfort all day long. The chair is upholstered in durable leatherette and features a steel alloy base. The office chair was designed by European custom automotive accessories designer Henri Lenterman. Has a lifetime warranty. The highest quality materials available. Can feel the quality in every piece of furniture they make.
description.930: Practical and adaptable for most office environments, mid-back office chairs are the logical choice for performing an array of tasks. A mid-back office chair offers support to the mid-to-upper back region. This chair is attractively designed with mesh inserts in the back and seat with vinyl surrounding. Chair easily swivels 360 degrees to get the maximum use of your workspace without strain. The pneumatic adjustment lever will allow you to easily adjust the seat to your desired height.
description.933: Enhance your work environment with the beautiful yet comfortable Z-Line Designs Executive Butterfly Bonded Leather Chair. This chair has a gorgeous design that looks great with many office settings. It is a great addition for any office. This chair is made from plastic, metal, and leather that make it robust and long lasting. It has a brown finish that looks great with any office decor. The upholstered chair is fire resistant that makes it safe for use. With a knee tilt mechanism, it also has contour seat and back with built-in lumbar support for exceptional functionality. The chair has butterfly seat plate with deluxe memory foam that provides you with exceptional comfort when you rest on it. The pneumatic seat height adjustment gives perfect height as desired. It has supple dark brown bonded matching leather upholstered arm rests and luxurious leather on all seating surfaces that is ideal to give maximum relaxation. The waterfall seat edge provides enhanced leg circulation. There are dual wheel carpet casters that allow easy mobility in the area. This Executive Butterfly Bonded Leather Chair from Z-Line Designs has a five-star champagne finished base with scuff resistant caps. It requires minor assembly before it can be used.
description.937: Update your office with this pneumatic height adjustable seat.
description.941: Work Smart by Office Star offers sleek and professional looking chairs that are a perfect finish for your office set up. Ventilated seating is the most stylish way to stay comfortable at your desk all day! With breathable fabric, users can easily stay dry and cool!
description.942: Work with utmost comfort with the Merax Leather Back Bonded Office Chair with Curved and Padded Arms. This luxurious office chair provides lumbar support and ensures you have a comfortable seating experience always. The seat, back and, arms of the chair are cushioned with high-quality foam and covered in bonded leather. This Leather Back Bonded Office Chair with Curved and Padded Arms by Merax has a height adjustable swivel base, so you can angle it right to find your perfect position. The chair offers complete back support and features padded armrests too. As it stands on five casters, the chair ensures ease at mobility. This modern office chair has a metal base and is completed with bonded leather. The chair is strong, sturdy, and has a weight limit of over 250 pounds. This modern-style executive chair is available in black and looks sophisticated. This high back office chair is height adjustable for a comfortable and personalized seating. The office chair is easy to clean and maintain. Regularly wipe the office chair with a clean, dry cloth and it will look new for years to come. This office chair can be quickly assembled in just a couple of minutes with the help of a screwdriver.
description.944: Sleek and contemporary this office chair provides comfort and function with Sealy Posturpedic™ Memory Foam. The foam conforms and evenly distributes weight supporting the body over complete contact area. This eliminates hard pressure points reducing stress and strain on the body while relieving seating fatigue and increasing comfort level.
description.945: The Corsica Chair has a deep cushioned seat and a back in black leather. There is a swivel seat with pneumatic height adjustment. It has a deluxe knee tilt control, a wood five star base, solid wood armrests with Black leather padding, and a tilt tension and tilt lock.
description.948: Task chair offers maximum comfort, support and functionality and minimizes the impact on your bottom line. The high-quality materials and customizable controls make it a smart solution for any application. Distinctive, ergonomic design reflects advanced comfort research. T-shaped back reduces pressure points while it supports the upper body. Light-scale visual effect fits well in the shrinking workplace. Bold styling and durable construction combine to deliver great value. Polyester fabric is abrasion-resistant for durability. Functions include 360-degree swivel and pneumatic seat-height adjustment from 16.5" to 21.12". Seat measures 19" wide x 18" deep. Back size is 18.75" wide x 17.5" high. Weight capacity is 250 lb. Five-star plastic base is equipped with dual-wheeled carpet caster for easy mobility. Arms are sold separately and adjust in width and height to maximize comfort.
description.950: Practical and adaptable for most office environments, mid-back office chairs are the logical choice for performing an array of tasks. description.951: Having a comfortable and an adaptable chair is a must for anyone in the office world today and Boss seems to satisfy this need with this contemporary piece.
description.952: Take the high road with this stellar drive toward productivity. Trendsetter sets your day in motion with fashionable rounded arms and padding you can sink into. The ergonomic office chair also comes with lumbar support, pneumatic height adjustment, a black nylon base, dual wheel carpet casters and a full 360 degree swivel.
description.954: Update your office chair with this high back pneumatic height-adjustable seat.
description.955: Vue™ life from a new perspective, one of comfort, performance and design. Vue™ chairs are the ultimate in extended-height seating. Rated for 24/7 use, the mesh back has ample support and ergonomic shaping to provide all day comfort and prevent fatigue. The breathability of the mesh keeps you cool and comfortable throughout every workday no matter how many hours you put in. 350 lb. weight capacity. Overall height is 39- 48 1/2". Reinforced mechanism with back tilt. Also includes back height adjustment, height adjustable footring and optional T-pad height and width adjustable arms Model 3399BL (sold separately).
description.956: Saddle Chair designed with durable vinyl cushion with polished aluminum frame and star base.
description.959: Designed to relieve all the tension points on your body. Thick, wrap around headrest sweeps across the wide top of the chair and down the sides. Lumbar support takes all pressure off your lower back and spine. Seat cushion slider adjusts to the length of your legs allowing for better blood circulation reducing or eliminating leg cramps. A magnificent chair designed to bring you pleasure every time you use it.
description.962: Add comfort to your daily work with the Rosewill Mid-Back Manager Chair. This premium chair comes equipped with 4-point PP armrests and a seat to ergonomically support your arms and body, increasing comfort and reducing fatigue. The durable 5-star nylon base with 2" hooded carpet casters can stand up to heavy-duty loads for enhanced stability and durability. Get this great chair today and enjoy your daily work in a comfortable way.rroro
description.968: The Canjun Office Chair is a beautifully crafted chair that works in any and every office space. The chair and arm rest are comfortably upholstered and constructed with a sturdy Chrome-Aluminum frame with wheel casters. It features adjustable tilt tension control and lift adjustable seat height. This chair will brighten any room and features executive styling that will be ideal in modern, open spaces.
description.970: This drafting chair has been tested to hold up to 400 lbs.! Not only will this chair hold the above average person, but it is amazingly comfortable. Chair will appeal for users of all heights and weights because of its comfort and sturdy construction. Chair has several adjustable functionalities so users can achieve their custom fit. The height adjustable arms are an added bonus to add to the appeal of this chair. Personalize this chair with custom text or a logo to show off your individual style or company design.
description.972: When you want a focused group of products designed to bring you the very best value for your furniture dollar, look to the Basyx by Hon collection. Basyx by Hon covers the gamut as from chairs and desks to storage and tables, and delivers a professional look on a budget. The new executive, task, and guest chairs from Basyx are styled for the needs of the contemporary office. And all are backed by the reliability and reputation of the Hon Company. Take a look! Nowhere else will you find this much product with this much value.
description.973: Add a functional yet comforting touch to your working area with the stylish Hazelwood Home High-Back Executive Chair with Arms. This chair has a great design that makes it fit any style setting perfectly. It is a comfortable chair with a nice appeal. It is made from plastic and faux leather that make it strong and long lasting. It has a black and silver finish that will enhance the look of your decor. This chair is durable and adorable as well. The chair has upholstered seat and backrest with padded cushion that provides you with maximum comfort when you rest on it. This chair works on lever mechanism with swivel that makes it a year-round chair for maximum relaxation during hectic working hours. The chair has height adjustability and swivels for great practicality. It has high-back that provides optimal comfort on the back and makes your working experience relaxing. There are hooded wheel casters that allow easy mobility in the area. This High-Back Executive Chair with Arms from Hazelwood Home can be wiped cleaned with a dry cloth. It has a weighing capacity of 250 pounds and requires minor assembly.
description.976: Work areas need practical seating answers. ComforTask delivers-no questions asked. This task chair features sculpted, molded backs with integral lumbar support.
description.979: With its elegant lines and wide variety of color and design options, extremely versatile Maui Chair easily meets needs of commercial and residential settings alike. Gently flared polypropylene seat is attached to light chrome-plated steel structure with five legs, adding mobility and practicality to its polished appearance. Maui chairs function well in any number of communal areas, from offices, classrooms and restaurants to dining rooms and bedrooms. In addition, Maui chairs meet CAL 133 fire code regulations and come in number of subdued as well as bold matte colors, making them ideal for businesses.
description.983: An economical choice for mesh comfort. Designed for the petite user, but adjustable to fit all. Three-lever multifunction mechanism for complete control of the back angle relative to seat, seat slide and forward tilt. Adjustable height back with adjustable lumbar support. Height- and width- adjustable arms with soft polyurethane armcaps for ideal arm placement. Black five-star nylon base with hooded casters. Tilt lock and tilt tension controls rate of recline to accommodate any user.
description.985: Volt seating from HON offers upscale style, full-scale comfort and impressive quality at a surprisingly affordable price. Its generously proportioned seat and back cushions are contoured to accommodate almost any body type. The visual design has a geometric flair that belies its affordable price. The easy-to-use adjustments put personalized comfort within reach. To look sharp, stay comfy and pay less, look to Volt.
description.986: Practical and adaptable for most office environments, mid-back office chairs are the logical choice for performing an array of tasks. A mid-back office chair offers support to the mid-to-upper back region. This chair is attractively designed with mesh inserts in the back and seat with vinyl surrounding. Chair easily swivels 360 degrees to get the maximum use of your workspace without strain. The pneumatic adjustment lever will allow you to easily adjust the seat to your desired height.
description.988: The RiteOne was designed for the office environment where modern styling combined with advanced ergonomic comfort and support are required.
description.989: The Series 300 High-Back has a thickly padded contoured leather seat and back, padded leather loop armrests, a deluxe knee-tilt control, and a pronounced lumbar support.
description.991: Regarded as one of the most iconic designer office chairs of the modern classics, this piece adds weight and poise to your office. With superior comfort as well as style, this chair is worthy of its fame and perfect for the discerning business.
description.996: This modern office chair features a leatherette seat and back in your choice of color. Its leather is perfectly complemented by a chromed steel frame and an aluminum base and armrests. This high back office chair conveniently tilts and swivels. It also features a knee tilt mechanism and a gas lift making it easily height adjustable. The high back office chair's quality construction makes it suitable for commercial use.
description.1001: Add style and substance to the office decor with the Hokku Designs Delta High-Back Mesh Office Chair with Arms. This office chair has a modern design that makes it suitable for different types of office decors.Made with metal and plastic, the base of the chair is durable and long-lasting. The seat is made from premium-quality material, which provides comfort to the user. This office chair has a back support that is made from mesh. It enhances the aesthetic appeal of the chair. This chair is available in an elegant black finish that complements the office decor. The arms of the chair provide support and comfort to the user. The legs are equipped with casters that ensure mobility to the chair. These casters are ideally suited for hard floors to ensure easy mobility. The lock-adjustment and swivel feature highlight the ergonomic factor of the office chair. For the comfort and convenience of the users, the height of the chair can be easily adjusted.The Delta High-Back Mesh Office Chair with Arms from Hokku Designs makes a fine addition to your study. This office chair can be easily wiped clean using a soft dry cloth. This ensures easy maintenance and makes the chair look new for a longer time.
description.1002: The Foster Desk Chair is a beautiful rustic industrial piece to add to your office for comfort and functionality. It is made from top grain leather, fireproof foam as well as wood and iron framing.
description.1005: Promotes interaction and collaboration. Flex Back and Flex Top created from high performance elastomer facilitates changes in posture and position throughout the work day. Extends range of movement, allowing you to sit comfortably in any position - even sideways. Flex net enables side-to-side flex and ensures optimal localized support for shoulders and lumbar region. High performance arms incorporate free-floating arm pads that naturally adjust as you change positions. Dynamic Suspension control counterbalances body weight, resulting in smooth, effortless ride. Tilt preference selector allows for additional resistance in recline.The Generation Chair is Greenguard certified. The Generation Chair has earned the Sustainable Platinum rating under SMaRT Consensus. Each authentic product includes a certificate of authenticity. The Generation Chair is the first chair that lets you sit how you want. It offers a new standard of comfort and unrestrained movement, supporting a range of postures and work styles typical of today's workplace. The Generation takes the idea of elastic design - where a product rearranges itself in response to user - to a new level. Form way Studios joined forces to create a chair that moves as you move, without forcing you to choose between freedom of movement and continuous support.It's not a chair. It's a movement.

First pre-assemble the chair without screws
Once assembled, loosely put each screw in and turn it one or two turns
Once all screws are inserted, tighten all the screws half way then go back and tighten all the screws again
NOTE: If one screw is tightened completely before the others, some of the pieces might not align properly and the last screw may not fit
Ball should be filled between 45cm to 50cm diameter; with 48cm being the best diameter. Measure the diameter from the North Pole to the South Pole with a tape measure or a string that is marked in Centimeters. This would be from where you fill the ball on the top to the bottom and you will see where the point should be by the center of the smallest circle. If the ball does not get to 45cm, let it sit for at least 24 hours then continue to fill again

LiveLumbar™ System: Allows user to experience continuous back surface support. Offers dialed in spring force in lumbar region actively supports lower back and can be adjusted to match user's anatomy
Synchro-Tilt System: chair back and seat are synchronized to move in 2:1 ratio. As user leans back, seat rises only half as much, allowing user's feet to remain flat on floor
Height, width, depth, and pivot arms: Arms telescope in and out, move forward and back, pivot and adjust up and down so you can find natural position comfortably supports wrists, forearms, shoulders and neck
Passive seat edge: When you recline or lean forward, seat edge flexes to relieve pressure on back of legs
Back tension controls: Allows user to set amount of ''push back'' desired when reclining, regardless of body size
Seat pan angle: -3°- +3°

Fabric: Use vacuum cleaner for regular cleaning
Do not steam clean

All materials in Amia chair were required to pass materials chemistry analysis by MBDC, which tests each substance for safety to human and environmental health
Up to 34% recyclable, made with up to 97% recycled content, avoided use of inseparable mixed materials to make recycling easier
Amia earned Gold Cradle to Cradle™ Product Certification from MBDC for using environmentally safe and renewable materials
Amia has Indoor Advantage™ Gold certification for protecting indoor air quality
Adjustable seat depth: People don't fit neatly into average body sizes. Leg and torso lengths can vary independent of person's overall height. Adjustable seat depth accommodates different body shapes for long-term comfort

A.) Your Profile™ Seat and Back
Back flexors track with the individual movement of your spine and pelvis. The back flexors are individually shaped to the human form to provide optimum support for each area of the back. Seat flexors conform to your shape, providing a dynamic comfort pocket. 
B.) Your Power™ Mechanism
The Your Power Mechanism moves as fluidly as the human body does. It provides recline support in proportion to your own body weight, while keeping you oriented to your work. 
C.) Height, Depth, Width, and Pivot Arms
Arms telescope in and out, move forward and back, pivot and adjust up and down so you can find a natural position that comfortably supports the wrists, forearms, shoulders and neck. 
D.) Flexible Seat Edge
When you recline or lean forward, the seat edge flexes to relieve pressure on the back of the legs. 
E.) Your Preference™ Control
The Your Preference Control combines four comfort settings into one simple dial. Select your favorite setting: weight activated, weight activated with at 20% boost, mid-stop recline, and upright back lock

Leap® is made from powder-coated steel, glass reinforced nylon, polypropylene, and leather
Plastic and painted parts: clean often using household cleaner (Fantastik® or 409®) and wipe with soft, dry cloth
Leather: Dust occasionally with clean, dry cloth
Most stains can be removed by applying mild soap to slightly damp cloth, then rubbing it gently over stain. Wipe dry
The Leap® chair is up to 98% recyclable by weight, depending on options selected, and made of up to 30% recycled content
Leap® manufacturing uses powder-coated paints, water-based adhesives and VOC-free manufacturing processes
The cushioning in back upholstery is made from 50% post-consumer PET (for example, recycled plastic soda and water bottles) and is 100% recyclable
Leap® is GREENGUARD Indoor Air Quality Certified
To reduce packaging waste, Leap® chair is blanket wrapped (not boxed) for domestic shipment. And throughout manufacturing process, our suppliers use reusable parts containers to further reduce waste
Through implementing leaner manufacturing processes, we were able to reduce amount of manufacturing space used to produce Leap® by 74%, resulting in significant reduction in amount of energy used in production
Please Note: Use of standard carpet casters on hard surfaces, including floor mats, will affect chair stability and may result in personal injury
The Leap chair is designed for a long life. To ensure that happens, back cushions, seat assembly, arms, and lumbar support can be added, changed, or replaced at any time
Frame and structural components (base, arms, seat, and back) – Lifetime (for as long as you own it), seating mechanisms, including pneumatic cylinders –10 years, fabric or Leather – 5 Years

Ergonomic Functions: A.) Live Back®The Leap chair's back changes shape to support the entire spine. This can reduce the chance of lower back sag and a hunched posture, which may weaken disc walls, stress back ligaments and cause deterioration of the spine. B.) Thermal Comfort Thanks to upholstered in both its back and seat, and the special foam it uses, the Leap chair offers excellent ''breathability''. It effectively controls a balance of heat and moisture so you stay comfortable. C.) Adjustable Seat - People don't fit neatly into average body sizes. Leg and torso lengths can vary independent of a person's overall height. Adjustable seat accommodates different body shapes for long-term comfort. D.) Lower Back Firmness Lower back firmness control enables you to set a constant amount of firmness to help maintain your lower spine's natural curve. E.) Height, D, W, and Pivot Arms Arms telescope in and out, move forward and back, pivot and adjust up and down so you can find a natural position that comfortably supports the wrists, forearms, shoulders and neck. F.) Natural Glide System™ As you recline, the seat glides forward so you can recline without leaving your Vision and Reach Zone, so you stay oriented to your work. This encourages more varied postures so there's less static load on the spine. G.) Flexible Seat Edge When you recline or lean forward, the seat edge flexes to relieve pressure on the back of the legs. H.) Upper Back Force Upper back force control enables you to set the amount of ''push back'' that you desire as you recline, regardless of body size. So you'll receive just the right amount of recline support.
Leap is made from powder-coated steel, glass reinforced nylon, polypropylene, and 100% polyester fabric

Leap manufacturing uses powder-coated paints, water-based adhesives and VOC-free manufacturing processes
The cushioning in the back upholstery is made from 50% post-consumer PET (for example, recycled plastic soda and water bottles) and is 100% recyclable
To reduce packaging waste, the Leap chair is blanket wrapped (not boxed) for domestic shipment. And throughout the manufacturing process, our suppliers use reusable parts containers to further reduce waste
Through implementing leaner manufacturing processes, we were able to reduce the amount of manufacturing space used to produce Leap by 74%, resulting in a significant reduction in the amount of energy used in production

696:
Features

Refined iconic design
Amazing ergonomic comfort
Upholstered seat and inner back
Plastic outer back, frame and base
Thermal Comfort design offers excellent ''breathability''
Patented ''live back'' technology supports entire spine
Natural Glide System allows reclining without disrupting work
Upper Back Force control customizes level of ''push back'' when reclining
Variable back stop with five recline angle positions
Flexible seat edge relieves pressure on back of legs
Lower back firmness control
Fully adjustable arms with pivot and soft caps for comfort
Adjustable seat depth
Pneumatic adjustable seat height
Soft, dual-wheel casters are available for use on hard wood floors or chair mats
Winner of numerous awards including NeoCon's Most Innovative Design Award and the Wall Street Journal's Best Overall Desk Chair
Has been tested for up to 300 lbs
LiveBack®: The Leap chair's back changes shape to support the entire spine. This can reduce the chance of lower back sag and a hunched posture, which may weaken disc walls, stress back ligaments and cause deterioration of the spine
Thermal Comfort: Thanks to upholstered in both its back and seat, and the special foam it uses, the Leap chair offers excellent ''breathability''. It effectively controls a balance of heat and moisture so you stay comfortable
Lower Back Firmness: Lower back firmness control enables you to set a constant amount of firmness to help maintain your lower spine's natural curve
Height, Depth, Width, and Pivot Arms: Arms telescope in and out, move forward and back, pivot and adjust up and down so you can find a natural position that comfortably supports the wrists, forearms, shoulders and neck
Natural Glide System™: As you recline, the seat glides forward so you can recline without leaving your Vision and Reach Zone, so you stay oriented to your work. This encourages more varied postures so there's less static load on the spine
Flexible Seat Edge: When you recline or lean forward, the seat edge flexes to relieve pressure on the back of the legs
Upper Back Force: Upper back force control enables you to set the amount of ''push back'' that you desire as you recline, regardless of body size. So you'll receive just the right amount of recline support
Seat Pan Angle: -1 - 3 degrees
Leap is made from powder-coated steel, glass reinforced nylon, polypropylene, and 100% polyester fabric
Plastic and painted parts: clean often using household cleaner (Fantastik® or 409®) and wipe with a soft, dry cloth
Fabric: Use a vacuum cleaner for regular cleaning
Do not steam clean
Most stains can be removed by applying a mild soap to a slightly damp cloth, then rubbing it gently over the stain. Wipe dry
The Leap chair is up to 98% recyclable by weight, depending on the options selected, and made of up to 30% recycled content
Environmental Information: Leap manufacturing uses powder-coated paints, water-based adhesives and VOC-free manufacturing processes.
The cushioning in the back upholstery is made from 50% post-consumer PET (for example, recycled plastic soda and water bottles) and is 100% recyclable
To reduce packaging waste, the Leap chair is blanket wrapped (not boxed) for domestic shipment. And throughout the manufacturing process, our suppliers use reusable parts containers to further reduce waste
Through implementing leaner manufacturing processes, we were able to reduce the amount of manufacturing space used to produce Leap by 74%, resulting in a significant reduction in the amount of energy used in production
Leap is GREENGUARD Indoor Air Quality Certified
Please Note: Use of standard carpet casters on hard surfaces, including floor mats, will affect chair stability and may result in personal injury
Adjustable Seat Depth: People don't fit neatly into average body sizes. Leg and torso lengths can vary independent of a person's overall height. Adjustable seat depth accommodates different body shapes for long-term comfort
The Leap chair is designed for a long life. To ensure that happens, back cushions, seat assembly, arms, and lumbar support can be added, changed, or replaced at any time
